divs: Sighting DetailsWas outside of my home, with my husband just got out of the car. Had my camera with me. Didn't have time to set up the camera or tripod, it was flying so fast. Held the tripod by the legs to capture it! This does not look man made. In fact I have about a dozen videos of simliar spheres,brillant, with blue light, green and red. The difference is that this one is static!
trends: There have been 34 other sightings in Overland Park

Summary: Large Sphere/UFO flying over my home
